*dnrd-2.20.3 (22 Mar 2007)

  22 Mar 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  -dnrd-2.20.ebuild, -dnrd-2.20.1.ebuild, +dnrd-2.20.3.ebuild:
