  proxy-maintain with Natanael Copa

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  05 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> dnrd-2.20.ebuild,
  dnrd-2.20.1.ebuild:
  Remove gnuconfig_update usage, leave it to econf.

  22 Oct 2006; Thomas Cort <tcort@gentoo.org> dnrd-2.20.1.ebuild:
  Added ~amd64 keyword wrt Bug #127361.

*dnrd-2.20.1 (01 Jan 2006)

  01 Jan 2006; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> +dnrd-2.20.1.ebuild:
  Version bump to 2.20.1. Fixes bug #113995. Thanks to Natanael Copa for
  reporting.

*dnrd-2.20 (02 Sep 2005)

  02 Sep 2005; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> files/dnrd,
  -dnrd-2.19.1.ebuild, +dnrd-2.20.ebuild:
  Removed obsolete 2.19.1 version in favor of 2.20 version from bug #104150.
  Modified files/dnrd since --uid dnrd is default now.

  23 Aug 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> dnrd-2.19.1.ebuild:
  Use -1 instead of /bin/false on enewuser call.

  17 Aug 2005; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> dnrd-2.19.1.ebuild:
  Permissions fix for bug #102225.

*dnrd-2.19.1 (21 Jul 2005)

  21 Jul 2005; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> files/dnrd,
  -dnrd-2.17.2.ebuild, -dnrd-2.18.ebuild, +dnrd-2.19.1.ebuild:
  Fix for security bug #99520. Thanks to Anarchy for confirming ~ppc. Removed
  older vulnerable versions.

  19 Apr 2005; Elfyn McBratney <beu@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove retired developer from metadata.xml.

*dnrd-2.18 (11 Jan 2005)

  11 Jan 2005; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> +dnrd-2.18.ebuild:
  Version bump to 2.18. Added ~ppc keyword. Fixes bug #77379. Thanks to
  Natanael Copa for the ebuild.

  11 Jan 2005; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +files/dnrd, +files/dnrd.conf, +dnrd-2.17.2.ebuild:
